# Base URL of the backend API (AZTU-E-QRANT-BACK).
#
# IMPORTANT: the admin panel is a client-side SPA — this URL is called from the
# visitor's BROWSER, so it must be reachable from the browser. Never use
# localhost / 127.0.0.1 for a deployed build (that points at the visitor's own
# machine, not the server).
#
# Vite inlines VITE_* at BUILD time, so you must rebuild after changing this.
#   - Local dev:  http://127.0.0.1:8080  (see .env.development)
#   - Production: the backend's public URL, e.g. https://api-e-grant.aztu.edu.az
#     If the admin is served over HTTPS, this MUST be https:// too (mixed-content).
#
# For a production build, create .env.production with the real value, e.g.:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api-e-grant.aztu.edu.az
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8080
